# wunderlichCurve

- _wunderlichCurve(n)_

Answer the first _n_ terms of the Wunderlich serpentine type _010 101 010_ curve.

_x_-coordinates of the Wunderlich curve,
OEIS [A323258](https://oeis.org/A323258):

~~~spl svg=A oeis=A323258
87.wunderlichCurve
.column(1)
.discretePlot
~~~

![](Help/Image/wunderlichCurve-A.svg)

_y_-coordinates of the Wunderlich curve,
OEIS [A323259](https://oeis.org/A323259):

~~~spl svg=B oeis=A323259
87.wunderlichCurve
.column(2)
.discretePlot
~~~

![](Help/Image/wunderlichCurve-B.svg)

The Wunderlich curve:

~~~spl svg=C
972.wunderlichCurve.Line
~~~

![](Help/Image/wunderlichCurve-C.svg)

